# Data layer

## Networking

- Use Retrofit with OkHttp as in the existing stack.

## Models and errors

- Map DTOs to domain (or UI-ready domain) models before they leave the data layer.
- Never expose raw DTOs to the UI.
- Handle errors explicitly (sealed result types, `Result`, or the project’s established pattern).
